    'Manual verification can be added for critical fields where OCR confidence is low, handwriting is present, or audit accuracy matters.',
    'Metadata output can support DMS, EMR, ERP, cloud folders, compliance reviews, and internal audit retrieval.'
  ],
  costFactors: [
    'Simple OCR/searchable PDF is usually lighter than multi-field indexing and validation.',
    'Handwritten, old, faded, skewed, or mixed-language documents require more review effort.',
